    "As examples, some experiences aim to help users to reduce their stress or anxiety levels (Darnall et al. 2020; Rockstroh et al. 2019; Tinga et al. 2019), overcome personal fears such as public speaking (e.g., Liao et al. 2018) and phobias (e.g., Alvear-Suarez et al. 2019)."
